Velika glances toward Hana, then back at you. She leans in close. [flags.UVETO_FROZEN_RESCUE_TO_BAR
		|<i>“Gossiping about your gallant savior? Bold.”</i> She smirks. <i>“To answer your question: she’s a woman after my own heart.
		|<i>“Not the sort you gossip about loudly. She’s a woman after my own heart.
	] You don’t get that kind of stillness unless you’ve buried a few things deep... and made sure they stayed there.”</i> [flags.UVETO_FROZEN_RESCUE_TO_BAR
		|She pauses, amusement curling her lips. <i>“Guess you picked the right person to freeze in front of.”</i>
	]
